query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS pixel_users (
  id BIGINT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  pixelUserId VARCHAR(64) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  userId INT,
  firstSeen TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  lastSeen TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  totalEvents INT DEFAULT 0,
  totalSessions INT DEFAULT 0,
  totalRevenue DECIMAL(10,2) DEFAULT 0.00,
  deviceFingerprint VARCHAR(255),
  consentStatus ENUM('unknown', 'granted', 'denied') DEFAULT 'unknown',
  consentTimestamp TIMESTAMP NULL,
  privacyTier ENUM('strict', 'moderate', 'permissive') DEFAULT 'permissive',
  country VARCHAR(2),
  INDEX user_idx (userId),
  INDEX consent_idx (consentStatus),
  INDEX country_idx (country)
);
